<i>Just remember me when...</i>

82
00:04:23,307 --> 00:04:25,503
<i>We used to be friends</i>

83
00:04:25,588 --> 00:04:27,690
<i>A long time ago</i>

84
00:04:27,878 --> 00:04:29,903
<i>We used to be friends</i>

85
00:04:31,308 --> 00:04:33,783
